/*******************************************************************************

This file has been generated by SoftKernelGenerator and controls what
TintModes, BlendModes and PixelFormats are supported in software rendering as
well as what blit operations have custom/optimized implementations.

The more supported, the more code is generated, resulting in a larger binary.

Generating optimized blits for all possible combinations can result in tens of
thousands of optimized render loops, growing the size of WonderGUI by many
megabytes.

For modern desktop applications wg_softkernels_default.h/cpp provides a good
balance between size and performance, supporting everyting but only optimizing
most important blit operations.

********************************************************************************

SUPPORTED MODES AND FORMATS 

Tint modes:            None
                       Flat
                       (unsupported: GradientX GradientY GradientXY)

Blend modes:           Replace
                       Blend
                       Invert
                       (unsupported: Add Subtract Multiply Min Max Morph BlendFixedColor)

Source formats:        BGR_8_linear
                       BGRX_8_linear
                       BGRA_8_linear
                       Index_8_linear
                       (unsupported: BGR_8_sRGB BGRX_8_sRGB BGRA_8_sRGB Index_8_sRGB Index_16 Index_16_sRGB Index_16_linear Alpha_8 BGRA_4_linear BGR_565_linear RGB_565_bigendian RGB_555_bigendian Bitplanes_1 Bitplanes_2 Bitplanes_4 Bitplanes_5 Bitplanes_8 Bitplanes_A1_1 Bitplanes_A1_2 Bitplanes_A1_4 Bitplanes_A1_5 Bitplanes_A1_8 BGRX_8_linear BGRA_8_linear)

Destination formats:   BGR_8_linear
                       BGRX_8_linear
                       BGRA_8_linear
                       (unsupported: BGR_8_sRGB BGRX_8_sRGB BGRA_8_sRGB Index_16 Index_16_sRGB Index_16_linear Alpha_8 BGRA_4_linear BGR_565_linear RGB_565_bigendian RGB_555_bigendian Bitplanes_1 Bitplanes_2 Bitplanes_4 Bitplanes_5 Bitplanes_8 Bitplanes_A1_1 Bitplanes_A1_2 Bitplanes_A1_4 Bitplanes_A1_5 Bitplanes_A1_8 BGRX_8_linear BGRA_8_linear)


CUSTOM BLIT KERNELS DEFINITION #1

Operations:         StraightBlit
                    StraightTile
                    TransformBlitNearest
                    
Tint Modes:         None
                    Flat
                    
Blend Modes:        Replace
                    Blend
                    
Source Formats:     BGR_8_linear
                    BGRX_8_linear
                    BGRA_8_linear
                    Index_8_linear
                    
Destination Formats:BGR_8_linear
                    BGRX_8_linear
                    BGRA_8_linear
                    

*******************************************************************************/

